:R-HSA-9636003  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0008150 ;
        rdfs:comment        "DNA glycosylase activity of NEIL3 is involved in resolution (unhooking) of psolaren-induced interstrand crosslinks (ICLs), as well as abasic site-induced ICLs (AP-ICLs) in a Fanconia anemia (FA) pathway-independent fashion (Semlow et al. 2016, Martin et al. 2017)." ;
        rdfs:label          "NEIL3-mediated resolution of ICLs" ;
        dc:contributor      "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Reviewed: Zhou, Jia, 2019-02-11" ;
